    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very reliable; the engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are functioning as intended. The interior is clean with only minor signs of wear, and the exterior paint retains a nice shine, though you may find a few small blemishes consistent with careful regular use. This is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
      "price": 34000.0,
