    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical care and a refined aesthetic, it balances sophisticated performance with long-term reliability. We invite you to experience the caliber of this exceptional offering, which has been thoroughly vetted to meet our rigorous standards of excellence.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and I think you\u2019re going to love it. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. Whether you\u2019re heading to work or taking a road trip, it runs like a charm and feels great on the road. It\u2019s been well-cared for and is ready for its next adventure with you. Come check it out and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power unit utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to deliver a linear power band up to an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox, the mechanical engagement is unparalleled. The chassis retains its composure via the M-Variable differential lock and aluminum multi-link rear suspension. Recent preventative maintenance includes updated rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring the longevity of the valvetrain and bottom end. The exterior displays minor road rash consistent with use, but the structural integrity and subframe mounting points are sound. This is a mechanically honest example ready for the apex.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title. Reliable engine. Minor cosmetic wear only.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior is finished in a deep metallic paint that still catches the light beautifully, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a quiet sanctuary; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free with all electronic components, including the dual-zone climate control and premium audio system, functioning perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs smoothly without any unusual noises or leaks. I have strictly adhered to the manufacturer's service schedule, and I have a folder of receipts to prove it, including a recent brake service and a new set of all-season tires with plenty of tread remaining. The transmission shifts crisply, and the suspension provides a firm yet comfortable ride. This car has been smoke-free and garage-kept, ensuring it remains in great shape for its next owner. It comes complete with two sets of keys and the original owner\u2019s manual.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle is offered in commendable condition. It has been maintained to a high standard, ensuring both mechanical reliability and a sophisticated aesthetic presence. This acquisition represents a superior value proposition for the driver who demands consistent performance and enduring quality. We invite serious inquiries regarding this well-preserved specimen.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m super excited to find a new home for this awesome ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really wonderful shape. It runs smoothly and has been well-loved and maintained, so it's totally ready for all your upcoming adventures. There\u2019s plenty of life left in this beauty, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love getting behind the wheel as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving valvetrain remains crisp, and the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise engagement. It features a limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery and has undergone critical preventive maintenance, including VANOS servicing and rear subframe reinforcement. While the aesthetic shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical fundamentals\u2014including the suspension bushings and cooling system\u2014are dialed in for spirited performance.",
